<figureCitation box="[159,294,798,823]" captionStart-0="FIGURES 53 – 61" captionStart-1="FIGURES 62 – 74" captionStartId-0="11.[151,264,1412,1435]" captionStartId-1="12.[151,264,1852,1875]" captionTargetBox-0="[191,1402,237,1357]" captionTargetBox-1="[198,1346,249,1792]" captionTargetId-0="figure@11.[151,1436,193,1392]" captionTargetId-1="figure@12.[176,1396,193,1838]" captionTargetPageId-0="11" captionTargetPageId-1="12" captionText-0="FIGURES 53 – 61. Acrogonia tenuis sp. nov. 53, body, male holotype (DZUP), dorsal view (total length 8.5 mm); 54, body, male holotype, lateral view; 55 – 61, male genitalia: 55, pygofer, lateral view; 56, subgenital plates, ventral view; 57, subgenital plate and part of style, lateral view; 58, styles and connective, dorsal view; 59, aedeagus and its basal processes, lateral view; 60, aedeagus and its basal processes, ventral view; 61, anal tube, lateral view. Scale bars: 55 = 1 mm; 56 – 61 = 0.5 mm." captionText-1="FIGURES 62 – 74. Acrogonia tenuis sp. nov., female. 62, sternite VII, ventral view; 63, pygofer, lateral view; 64, first valvifer and first valvula, lateral view; 65, basal lobe of first valvula; 66, dorsal sculptured area at basal portion of blade; 67, dorsal sculptured area at median portion of blade; 68, ventral sculptured area; 69, apical portion of blade; 70, second valvula, lateral view; 71, teeth at basal portion of blade; 72, teeth at median portion of blade; 73, teeth at apical portion of blade; 74, apical third of blade. Scale bars: 62 – 64, 70 = 1 mm. BBS: basimedian bifurcated structure, BLB: basal lobe, LPR: lateral projection, VPR: ventral projection." httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/437250/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/437251/files/figure.png" pageId="10" pageNumber="525">Figs. 53–74</figureCitation>
